---------------------------------- CODE 
/*

GarageCode coolest things Hehehe
http://GarageCode.tk

*Function this programm
this simple Daemon Shell in C language with fork 

*tested with GCC 
 i wheel on Unix/Linux/BSD this:
    gcc -o program program.c; ./program

Author: &quot;Cooler_&quot;  
